precis:
Authority to enter in an AGREEMENT with the City of Montreal concerning the
making of a financial contribution towards the restoration and outfitting
of an interpretation centre focusing on the ecosystem of the Great Lakes
and the St. Lawrence River that is to be located in the MONTREAL BIOSHPERE
on St. Helen Island.
